comments: This professor is the reason that I want to change my major. She taught 3 of my classes in 1 semester in which I had to teach myself EVERYTHING. Would make us sit in a classroom across from her on Wimba even though UDM\'s bandwidth is not large enough. Didn\'t prepare me for later classes whatsoever. I cannot believe that she still "teaches" at UDM.

Great if you want to learn nothing! She absolutely teaches nothing, period. Plan on hours of self teaching. No examples and relies on "Wimba" for her dumb on-line lectures. Stay away from Yost if you care about your education and life!!!!!!!!
